  "instructions": [
    "Thaw the prawns if frozen; rinse under cold water and pat dry.",
    "Slice the prawns into bite\u2011size cubes.",
    "In a bowl whisk together lemon juice, lime juice, olive oil, salt, pepper, cumin, coriander, garlic, and jalape\u00f1o.",
    "Add the diced onion and cilantro, then fold in the prawns, tossing to coat evenly.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for 30\u201345 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
